Raymond Walburn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Raymond_Walburn 0 Raymond Walburn (September 9, 1887 – July 26, 1969) was an American character actor of stage and screen who appeared in dozens of Hollywood movie comedies and an occasional dramatic role during the 1930s and 1940s.
